<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176692>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 11. Temnothorax workers, left: lateral view of body, right: full-face view of head. 2 & 3, T. alienus Holotype; 4 & 5, T. satunini, Prov. Artvin, East Turkey; 6 & 7, T. nylanderi, Beira Alta, Sierra de Montemuro, Portugal; 8 & 9, T. lichtensteini, Südtirol, Italy; 10 & 11, T. italicus, Island Krk, Kroatia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176692/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176694>
    dc:description "FIGURES 22 – 25. Temnothorax workers, dorsal views showing first gaster tergite, postpetiole, petiole and mesosoma. 22 T. alienus, Holotype; 23, T. saxatilis, Holotype; 24, T. nigriceps, Arcadia, Peloponnesos, Greece; 25, T. tuberum, Val di Fossa, Alto Edige, Italy." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176694/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176695>
    dc:description "FIGURES 26 – 27. Temnothorax gynes, lateral view of body. 26, T. alienus Holotype; 27, T. saxatilis Holotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176695/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.176696>
    dc:description "FIGURES 28 – 37. Temnothorax gynes, left: dorsal view of body. right: full-face view of head. 28 & 29, T. alienus Holotype; 30 & 31, T. nylanderi, Beira Alta, Sierra de Montemuro, Portugal; 32 & 33, T. saxatilis Holotyp; 34 & 35, T. nigriceps, Arcadia, Peloponnesos, Greece; 36 & 37, T. affinis, near Spitz, Wachau, Austria." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/176696/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

